Name: Maze Of The Gamja
About the game: About This Game Solve Gamja-puzzles and Acquire Gamja-knowledges! Maze Of The Gamja is a puzzle game that can be played with a keyboard or mouse. Move up, down, left, right, or activate the surrounding blocks to open a new path. Each action will reduce the count and all sweet potatoes must be obtained before the count reaches zero. There are 66 Gamja-puzzles, 193 Gamja-photos, and 75 Gamja-knowledge!
